## Act III: Writing That Leads the Way

### Quickstart Guide  
VuLink is powerful. And power comes with complexity. Thatâ€™s why I wrote a quickstart guide that could stand on its own.

Following Teslerâ€™s Law, I focused on reducing *perceived* complexity:
- Break each process into small, clear steps  
- Pair every step with a photo  
- Use plain, direct language throughout  

Itâ€™s possible to go from box to deployment using just this guideâ€”and many users do.

### Manual + FAQs  
For users who want more, I wrote a full manual and published it online. After launch, I worked with sales and support to collect real user questions and turn them into FAQs. These werenâ€™t just fillerâ€”they addressed setup blockers, common misconceptions, and real-world scenarios.

